Package: varmonitor
Type: Package
Title: Risk management tools: Value-at-Risk monitor
Version: 0.1.8
Date: 2021-05-08
Author: Gatti Riccardo, Lin Francesco
Maintainer: <fkl@francescolin.com>
Description: Given a portfolio of securities and their volatilities, the package provide tools to estimate the Value-at-Risk and Expected Shortfall according to the parametric and analytical approach under the following assumptions: no time-varying volatility; changes of the market variables are normally distributed.
License: GPL-3
